description	"Archetype: Imperial Director

Class Summary: 
A speedy commander with a high-powered pistol and defensive utilities.

Weaponry:
- DT-29 Pistol * 
- Quickthrow Grenade (1) (Does not appear in inventory, can only be quickthrown)
- Concussion Grenades (2)

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
---DT-29 Pistol
- High damage per shot
- Increased knockback per shot
- 6 shots per clip
- Magazine style reload

Inventory:
- Portable Sentry Gun
- Portable Shield

Attributes:
- Rally
- Regenerating Shields (1)

Abilities:
- Quickthrow (2)
- Dodge (3)
- Bounty Hunter style kicks and get-up rolls

~Orson Krennic: Director of the Advanced Weapons Research division of the Imperial Military and commander of the Death Star Battle Station up to the beginning of the Galactic Civil War.
----------
~Wilhulf Tarkin: A politician, bureaucrat, and military officer whose career spanned the Fall of the Republic and the Age of the Empire. He believed the Empire could terrify the galaxy into total submission."